##### Popular go check tools

# make go lang code style recommendation 
golint
golangci-lint run
ignore: //nolint
see doc: https://golangci-lint.run/usage/linters/

# apply standard formating
gofmt

# finds subtle issues 
go vet

# find serious erros from code running 
compiler

##### File is not gofmt-ed with -s 
 gofmt -s -w <>.go

 gofumpt -w filename


