### update go mod
Use go get xxxx@vxxx to update the go mod, if for private repository use this way
 - go env -w GOPRIVATE=github.com/EnterpriseDB/cloud-native-postgresql 
 - go get github.com/EnterpriseDB/cloud-native-postgresql@v1.13.0

golangci-lint run --fix

